Submission  of the course paper on comparative British and American studies - see Moodle for details
A-	the paper is presented on time; all tasks are completed in full with excellent  knowledge of background sources; it demonstrates  creative and independent thinking 
B-	the paper is presented on time; all tasks are completed with very good knowledge of background sources; it shows very good  ability of the student to apply theoretical knowledge in practice;
C-	the paper is presented on time; all tasks are completed with good knowledge of background sources; it shows good  ability of the student to apply theoretical knowledge in practice but lacks original thinking; 
D-	the paper is presented with delay; all tasks are completed with satisfactory  knowledge of background sources 
E-	the paper is presented with delay; tasks are completed with satisfactory to poor  knowledge of background sources.

